This is a great product, I’ve installed it myself and it’s been running for a few weeks now. It’s amazing to see the roof temp and how quickly it changes when cloud comes over, this is definitely keeping our pool warmer than when we were turning it on before work in the mornings and off just before dusk. Installation was easy with basic plumbing knowledge. The hardest part is finding the 22 gauge wire needed to run your roof sensor. No hardware or big box or electrical supply companies carry this wire. 22/2 all weather wire is hard to find. I called Pentair and they said find a 22/4 or 22/5 and just use 2 wires. Still easier said than done. Keep this in mind when ordering!
Great product, my previous pair lasted me well over 10 year and my insulated ones are approaching that as well and are still holding up.
